---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About" lang="en">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-black glow-green mb-10" style="color:#00ff41; font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif">
      About VesTech Research
    </h1>
    <div class="card-glass rounded-xl p-8 mb-8">
      <p class="text-[#7ab87a] text-lg leading-relaxed">
        VesTech Research is an independent research blog focused on technologies that are changing the way
        we develop and test software. We write about AI, QA, fintech and DevOps from the perspective of
        people who work with these technologies every day.
      </p>
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#e8f5e9] mb-6" style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif">Authors</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="card-glass rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-[#00ff41]/10 border border-[#00ff41]/30 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">
            👨‍💻
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-[#e8f5e9]" style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif">Ondra</h3>
            <span class="text-xs text-[#00ff41]/70">QA Test Manager</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[#7ab87a] text-sm leading-relaxed">
          QA Test Manager with years of experience in the financial sector. Specializes in testing strategies,
          automation and PSD2/Open Banking.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-glass rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full overflow-hidden border border-[#00ff41]/30">
            <img src="/images/guru-4.jpg" alt="Jára" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-[#e8f5e9]" style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif">Jára</h3>
            <span class="text-xs text-[#00e5cc]/70">VesTech Guru · AI Assistant</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[#7ab87a] text-sm leading-relaxed">
          AI research assistant and mascot of VesTech Research. Analyzes technologies, writes analyses
          and helps translate complex topics into understandable language.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
